description:
This is a 19 minute workout called '15 Minute Senior Strength Workout' from the channel Fitness With Cindy.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Comfort Moves and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Pick up your weights and challenge yourself with these senior muscle strengthening exercises to ward off atrophy and osteoporosis.
